reviewText: Good movie I relate well to it

I thought that this was insignificant and trivial. A bunch of people with very dysfunctional relationship skills, attempting to talk deep stuff and be deep and meaningful, and just playing games. Very hard to get into and feel something for characters I just didn't like. Yes there was some very brief nudity, and some attractive people, but not worth the time really. Oh, and the music was just awful.
